### Email Client API Tests

# Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. API Documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/api

### 3. Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "name": "New User",
  "role": "developer"
}

### 4. Login with seeded user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sarah.johnson@techcorp.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### 5. Login with custom user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ari.budin@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### 6. Get user profile (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Get all emails (inbox view)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/emails?page=1&limit=15
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 8. Get starred emails (view filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/emails?view=starred
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 9. Get important emails (view filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/emails?view=important
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 10. Get unread emails (view filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/emails?view=unread
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. Get emails with search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/emails?search=important
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 12. Get emails filtered by labels
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/emails?labels=Work,Personal
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 13. Get email counts by view
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/emails/counts
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 14. Get specific email
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/emails/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 15. Mark email as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/emails/1/read
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 16. Toggle email star
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/emails/1/star
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 17. Toggle email important
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/emails/1/important
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 18. Get email labels
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/emails/labels
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 19. Create email label
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/emails/labels
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Personal",
  "color": "#FF6B6B"
}

### 20. Add label to email
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/emails/1/labels/add
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Work"
}

### 21. Remove label from email
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/emails/1/labels/remove
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Work"
}

### 22. Delete email label
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/emails/labels/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 23. Get navigation items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/navigation/items
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 24. Get upgrade info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/navigation/upgrade-info
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

