Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 28. Mark all notifications as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/notifications/mark-all-read
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 29. Get messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/messages
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 30. Get unread message count
